nodes.bodyText:
This can be slightly simplified by using some() (which returns a boolean) instead of find().
Also imo the explicit boolean cast !! inside the callback is unnecessary in this case (but it's also ok).




        Suggested change











                return !!this[validatorsSymbol].find(val => !!val.impliesRequired);



                return this[validatorsSymbol].some(validator => validator.impliesRequired);

